  "detailed_description": "Bull Looney, changed by a UFO encounter, realizes his boo, Cow Bella, is in danger. Bull must find and save his sweetheart. Your journey starts here, so do your best to make a speedy get away!  In this 3rd person view, drive, smash, and dodge your way through to save Cow Bella all while avoiding kamikaze police, farmers, city people, and aliens! Your mission is to shut down the meat factory and finally try to escape by borrowing a UFO! Don't forget to pick up Cow Bella.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/e3965a125e0af85837863fdda0e4ca99.poster.avif?t=1721768288\" width=506 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/e3965a125e0af85837863fdda0e4ca99.webm?t=1721768288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/e3965a125e0af85837863fdda0e4ca99.mp4?t=1721768288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/baf883579c345d70c1876a2487c8489d.poster.avif?t=1721768288\" width=506 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/baf883579c345d70c1876a2487c8489d.webm?t=1721768288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/baf883579c345d70c1876a2487c8489d.mp4?t=1721768288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3029440/extras/1e26975b614e02f49427a54436a135b6.avif?t=1721768288\" width=458 height=474 /></span>",
